title: SwifTEA: A Vault Collab With Drake?!
description:
Drake's social media post can only mean one thing, right? Plus, Joe Alwyn speaks out about his relationship status. And paging Dr. Swift!
We also read some fan mail.. Hit us up with all of your thoughts and suggestions! There are lots of ways to reach us!
